articles.title: Thanksgiving bomb threats target Democrat lawmakers - Fox News
articles.description: Nationally syndicated reporter Salena Zito joins 'America's Newsroom' to discuss the threats against Trump nominees and six Democratic lawmakers and the anti-Israel protests targeting the Macy's parade.
